  "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\nNow we have many peers at regular sync times but still have few sync peers at regular sync time:\r\n```\r\n2020-10-15 15:03:15 [SYNC]             info: Peer status activePeers=21, syncPeers=2, unknownRootPeers=2\r\n2020-10-15 15:03:51 [SYNC]             info: Peer status activePeers=24, syncPeers=2, unknownRootPeers=2\r\n```\r\nWe should leverage our scoring system to disconnect bad peers and connect to new ones.\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\nHave a new task or leverage DiversifyPeersBySubnetTask starting from initial sync time, based on our peer scoring system to disconnect bad ones and connect to new ones.\r\n\r\nSome goodbye codes lighthouse had:\r\n```\r\n1 => GoodbyeReason::ClientShutdown,\r\n            2 => GoodbyeReason::IrrelevantNetwork,\r\n            3 => GoodbyeReason::Fault,\r\n            128 => GoodbyeReason::UnableToVerifyNetwork,\r\n            129 => GoodbyeReason::TooManyPeers,\r\n            250 => GoodbyeReason::BadScore,\r\n            251 => GoodbyeReason::Banned,\r\n```",
